These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, paramedic, dressmaker, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the dressmaker is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the dressmaker##6
5. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5
6. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | mechanic  | freelancer | dressmaker | paramedic  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, techno, punk, pop
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
3. the fan of blues is the journalist##1
4. the fan of pop is between the fan of blues and the fan of techno##2
5. the fan of techno is somewhere between the fan of punk and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk | techno          | pop | blues     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, august, february
1. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
7. the paramedic is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Birthday   | december    | february   | june | august    |

