.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero, horror, documentary
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
6. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the person watching documentary movies is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | documentary | martial-arts | superhero  | horror |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

