.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, subway, train
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, rugby, tennis
1. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person driving the bike##7
5. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
6. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person driving the subway##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Transport     | bike | subway | train | motorbike     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

