.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, coach, chef
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the chef##8
2. the dancer is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the photographer is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the dancer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the chef and the coach##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
