.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince, oliveros, bluemaster
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, family, superhero
 1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
 3. the dannemann-smoker is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 9. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the dannemann-smoker##8
10. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar          | prince    | oliveros | dannemann | bluemaster |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | superhero  | family     | crime    |

