.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, august, january
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, drawing, reading, video-games
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday    | january        | september | july | august |
| Hobby   | video-games | reading | drawing   | camping    |

