.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking fanta##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking sprite and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | sprite      | milk     | fanta     |

 